Former Missouri Auditor Tom Schweich shot himself in the head on February 26 . 
  He was running for governor in 2016 . 
  Schweich was upset about allegations of anti-Semitism in his own party . 
  He told an aide on the day of his death that he would have to 'run as an independent or he needed to kill himself' Schweich had talked for years about suicide but left no suicide note . 
  His spokesman Spence Jackson also killed himself a month later . 
 